<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Blockchain on Console Labs</title><link>https://log.console.so/tags/blockchain/</link><description>Recent content in Blockchain on Console Labs</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><managingEditor>han@console.so (Han Ngo)</managingEditor><webMaster>han@console.so (Han Ngo)</webMaster><copyright>© 2026 Console Labs.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://log.console.so/tags/blockchain/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Support Trending token</title><link>https://log.console.so/earn/support-trending-token/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>han@console.so (Han Ngo)</author><guid>https://log.console.so/earn/support-trending-token/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purpose&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the trending token for tip, deposit and withdraw on Mochi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Source of trending token&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
You can choose token to support from these source&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;From the /ticker and /watchlist add. Check out the suggested list &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1yNJnRNu85CLJ4dNI6LDkVU6IW10pzd8KgkceTauSZ_Q/edit#gid=1495581261"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.binance.com/en/markets/overview" title="https://www.binance.com/en/markets/overview"&gt;Binance&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/trending-cryptocurrencies/" title="https://coinmarketcap.com/trending-cryptocurrencies/"&gt;Coinmarketcap/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Twitter, hastag $&amp;hellip;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Token Priority to support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The most recent and queried token by Mochi user&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The token on the chain that we have supported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Token on Binance, CMC, Twitter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
